Are you as ready to hit the slopes as I am? Ski season is officially here! I’ve teamed up with @ogio to share the ONLY way I travel with my ski gear so I know it will arrive safely! All of this gear is also endorsed by the US Ski & Snowboard Team - so you know it’s the absolute best! 
 
You already know I only travel with #Ogio gear, from my weekly carry on, to golf equipment, and now my ski gear is protected and looks better than ever!  Want a set of your own? Ogio is giving away an item from our Snow Collection of your choosing to one of you lucky snow lovers! 
 
To enter you MUST:
- Follow @ogio & @lax.chelsea 
- Like this post
- Tag who you want to ride the chairlift with
- Bonus entry - tag your favorite ski / snowboard spot
 
Can’t wait to win! Don’t forget you can still get 25% off all Ogio products with code CHELSEA25 

(1 winner will be chosen at random and notified via @OGIO’s Verified DM on 12/16. Giveaway open until 12/15 at 11:59pm PST. Open U.S. + Canada only)

Looking forward to more adventures in 2023 ✨
